        a                        fabio:Figure ;
        dc:description           "Figures 13–18. Species habitus in the genus Acyphoderes. Figures 13–15. Acyphoderes hirtipes (Klug, 1825). 13) male. 14) female and 15) female Acyphoderes rufofemorata Fisher, 1930 (junior synonym). 16) Acyphoderes crinita (Klug, 1825), female. 17) Acyphoderes rubrohirsutotibialis Tippmann, 1953, female. 18) Acyphoderes auricapilla Fisher, 1947, female paratype." ;
